comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_LESS_LES_UNPEER_GROUP_STATE.afptentriskexpse
  is '潜在风险暴露-合计';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_LESS_LES_UNPEER_GROUP_STATE.bankacptdraft
  is '潜在风险暴露-其中：银行承兑汇票';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_LESS_LES_UNPEER_GROUP_STATE.documlc
  is '潜在风险暴露-其中：跟单信用证';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_LESS_LES_UNPEER_GROUP_STATE.bkltr
  is '潜在风险暴露-其中：保函';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_LESS_LES_UNPEER_GROUP_STATE.loanproms
